------------------------------------------------------------
ES6 FEATURES DEMONSTRATED
------------------------------------------------------------
  1. map()
     players.map((p, i) => <li>...</li>)
     → Renders all 11 players as list items

  2. filter() + arrow function
     players.filter(p => p.score < 70)
     → Returns: Shubman Gill(42), Shreyas Iyer(63),
       KL Rahul(55), Axar Patel(29), Jasprit Bumrah(11),
       Mohammed Shami(8), Kuldeep Yadav(15)

  3. Destructuring
     const [first, second, ...rest] = T20players
     → Odd Team: first + rest[0], rest[2]...
     → Even Team: second + rest[1], rest[3]...

  4. Spread / Merge
     const merged = [...T20players, ...RanjiTrophy]
     → 10-player merged array

